{"tid":532250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Volvo變中國公司後安全性受質疑，被奧迪撞竟斷成兩截","createTime":"2018-01-17T15:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T05:24:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cad51bfc2435f51cdf7e2150a9f3ed57d036408e","tid":532250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"January 17, 2018 admin  0 Comment<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/sketch-1516176861753.png?resize=1024%2C576\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fsketch-1516176861753.png%3Fresize%3D1024%252C576&h=e907e40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在瑞典成立的汽車品牌Volvo一直以安全作為賣點，多年來Volvo亦一再在各種交通意外中證明自己如何硬淨。可是自2010年公司將品牌售予中國的吉利汽車後，其質素便開始受到質疑。<br />\n<br />\n日前中國的汽車論壇上，有網民上傳自己的Volvo汽車被撞後的模樣，令不少網民感到吃驚，對其安全性的疑慮亦更深。<br />\n<br />\n據網民描述及圖片所示，出事的Volvo被一輛奧迪從側面撞倒後，居然斷成兩截!<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/593c0002203a7139fa1f.jpg?resize=640%2C589\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F593c0002203a7139fa1f.jpg%3Fresize%3D640%252C589&h=81a096b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件在論壇上引起不少迴響，有網民指自變成中國公司後，Volvo的「安全」已變成口號。面對排山倒海的質疑，不少論壇上相關的發帖已經被刪，有人懷疑是Volvo公關所為，令人感覺更欲蓋彌彰。"},{"pid":"ae202cdea940543977eb5ff2de17b42f60c5d9e5","tid":532250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=9801#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D9801%23&d=ylOtWB8qs9gat1RKTDBNC26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f0035aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=9801#</a>"},{"pid":"182f446c3c252a01176cbb41375f33f57074db2a","tid":532250,"uid":51134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:01:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_A9A7wttUqw\